      <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-mist">
        Good continuity reduces orientation cost. It helps the agent recover its own thread instead of making the human rebuild that thread by hand after every interruption.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-canopy bg-undergrowth/30 p-7">
      <p class="font-display text-xl italic text-bone">What to ask next</p>
